Auto Staging System
by mmd

Kerbal Space Program 0.20
MonoDevelop 4
GPLv3


INSTRUCTIONS:
[1] compile the class library into autostage.dll
[2] place dll into Plugins/ directory
[3] create a custom part in GameData/Squad/Parts (can just make a copy of existing part)
[3] edit part.cfg and set module = AutoStage under general parameters
[4] include the part in your rocket in VAB
[5] once on the lanchpad, a GUI window should appear which allows setting altitude and thrust of each automatic staging point
[6] press TOGGLE to activate the auto staging
